e>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die statische <code><strong>Atomics</strong></code><strong><code>.exchange()</code></strong> Methode ersetzt einen Wert an einer gegebenen Position im einem Array mit einem gegebene Wert aus. Die atomare Operation garantiert, dass kein anderer Schreibprozess während der Operation durchgeführt wird.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/atomics-exchange.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">Atomics.compareExchange(typedArray, index, value)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"typedarray\"><code>typedArray</code></dt>\n <dd>Ein geteiltes getrypted Integer Array. Eines von <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int8Array\"><code>Int8Array</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>Uint8Array</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int16Array\"><code>Int16Array</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>Uint16Array</code></a>, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Int32Array\"><code>Int32Array</code></a> oder <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>Uint32Array</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"index\"><code>index</code></dt>\n <dd>Die Position in <code>typedArray</code>, an den ein Wert ersetzt wird.</dd>\n <dt id=\"value\"><code>value</code></dt>\n <dd>Neu Zahl, die geschreiben wird.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Der alte Wert an der gegebenen Position (<code>typedArray[index]</code>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"Exceptions","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Erzeugt einen <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a>, wenn <code>typedArray</code> nicht von einem erlaubten Integer Typ ist.</li>\n <li>Erzeugt eine <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a>, wenn <code>typedArray</code> kein geteilter Arraytyp ist.</li>\n <li>Erzeugt ein <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>RangeError</code></a>, wenn der <code>index</code> nicht in den Grenzen von <code>typedArray</code> ist.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> sab <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SharedArrayBuffer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1024</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ta <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Uint8Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>sab<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nAtomics<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">compareExchange</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ta<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">12</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// returns 0, the old value</span>\nAtomics<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">load</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>ta<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 12</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-atomics.exchange\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Atomics.exchange' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initiale Definition in ES2017.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Atomics.exchange","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/exchange/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics\"><code>Atomics</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/compareExchange\"><code>Atomics.compareExchange()</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die statische Atomics.exchange() Methode ersetzt einen Wert an einer gegebenen Position im einem Array mit einem gegebene Wert aus. Die atomare Operation garantiert, dass kein anderer Schreibprozess während der Operation durchgeführt wird.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Atomics.exchange()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Atomics.exchange()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Atomics.exchange()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Atomics.exchange()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/atomics/exchange","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/atomics/exchange/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript-Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Globale Objekte"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics","title":"Atomics"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Atomics/exchange","title":"Atomics.exchange()"}],"pageTitle":"Atomics.exchange() - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}